  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.ityx.contex.interfaces.white.Licensable, IContent, IEmail, IEmailCompact, IErpsData, IProjectRelation, Serializable

    public class Emaillist
extends Question
    The email lists are used to sent e.g. advertising emails to the certain customers. Newsletters can be sent scheduled to the selected customers with the help of the emaillist.
